### Create Slot

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotDate": "2026-06-10",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "09:00:00",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Create Another Slot

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotDate": "2026-06-10",
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "10:00:00",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Get All Slots

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Slot By Id

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots/2
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Slot

PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotDate": "2026-06-15",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "11:00:00",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Verify Updated Slot

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots/2
Accept: application/json
